headline: Realtor.com® Unveils Realtor.com®+™: A First-of-Its-Kind Collaborative Home Search Experience
summary: Realtor.com® today announced the public debut of Realtor.com®+™, (pronounced "plus"), a collaborative home search platform built in collaboration with MLSs that helps real estate professionals and consumers connect, collaborate and close with confidence. Designed to elevate the search experience and strengthen MLS and professional value, Realtor.com®+™ sets a new standard for transparency, insights and agent-client collaboration.
